son of the sunshine is a canadian supernatural drama film . directed by ryan ward and written by ward and matthew &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , the film stars ward as sonny &lt;&lt;unk&gt;&gt; , a young man with tourette syndrome who undergoes an experimental surgical procedure to cure the condition , only to discover that he also loses his supernatural ability to heal others . the film premiered at slamdance film festival and other film festivals in 2009 , and had a general release in 2011 .